WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.699
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:01.599
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.732
=Episode 6=

00:01:13.059 --> 00:01:14.299
Let go.

00:01:23.125 --> 00:01:24.874
No matter when or where,

00:01:24.875 --> 00:01:26.516
once the jade whistle sounds,

00:01:26.699 --> 00:01:28.299
I will appear.

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:43.338
South Mountain. Hurry.

00:01:43.339 --> 00:01:45.120
The main force has not assembled yet.
Should we wait for them?

00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.000
There is no time.
Have them regroup at South Mountain.

00:01:54.059 --> 00:01:54.980
Who are you?

00:01:55.100 --> 00:01:56.019
Do not come any closer.

00:01:56.460 --> 00:01:58.179
Do you know who stands behind me?

00:01:59.987 --> 00:02:00.945
Do not come closer.

00:02:01.540 --> 00:02:02.511
Stay back.

00:02:02.512 --> 00:02:03.633
Stay back.

00:02:14.860 --> 00:02:16.778
You were never meant to be here today.

00:02:16.779 --> 00:02:17.761
Speak.

00:02:17.762 --> 00:02:19.340
What is your true purpose?

00:02:19.659 --> 00:02:21.232
I don't know
what you are talking about.

00:02:21.499 --> 00:02:22.859
Have you not suffered enough

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:24.379
up to this point?

00:02:24.619 --> 00:02:26.480
Shengtang Guild is different
from Huanyue House.

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:27.259
Before, perhaps,

00:02:27.260 --> 00:02:29.859
you could survive with a few tricks.

00:02:30.140 --> 00:02:32.324
But once you step through
the doors of Shengtang Guild,

00:02:32.325 --> 00:02:34.220
there is no turning back.

00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:36.379
You will never rise again.

00:02:39.939 --> 00:02:41.060
Get out of here.

00:03:10.900 --> 00:03:12.020
Gu Chengye.

00:03:13.460 --> 00:03:14.460
I told you,

00:03:14.499 --> 00:03:15.859
once the jade whistle sounds,

00:03:16.379 --> 00:03:18.379
I will be by your side.

00:03:43.659 --> 00:03:44.620
Tell me,

00:03:45.020 --> 00:03:46.780
which hand touched her?

00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:06.060
Gu Chengye,

00:04:06.099 --> 00:04:06.739
are you hurt?

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:08.699
I am fine. He did nothing.

00:04:11.300 --> 00:04:12.539
Let us move quickly.

00:04:16.099 --> 00:04:17.538
Big, big, big, big!

00:04:17.539 --> 00:04:18.699
I want this one.

00:04:18.700 --> 00:04:19.658
This, this, this!

00:04:19.659 --> 00:04:21.460
This is mine!

00:04:23.299 --> 00:04:25.179
How do you win every hand?

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:30.778
You are on quite a streak.

00:04:30.779 --> 00:04:31.658
It seems

00:04:31.659 --> 00:04:33.657
that this is the painter
at the Shengtang Guild.

00:04:34.580 --> 00:04:36.257
That high-ranking official said

00:04:36.339 --> 00:04:37.900
Shengtang Guild has a painter.

00:04:38.339 --> 00:04:39.700
The Beauty Portrait he draws

00:04:39.739 --> 00:04:41.780
records every transaction here.

00:04:48.500 --> 00:04:49.580
Official Leopard Cat,

00:04:49.700 --> 00:04:50.899
will you keep this courtesan

00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:52.619
or...

00:04:52.620 --> 00:04:53.460
I'll keep her.

00:04:54.580 --> 00:04:56.699
Your flower fee is three thousand taels.

00:04:56.700 --> 00:04:58.259
Shengtang Guild takes one-tenth.

00:04:58.260 --> 00:04:59.859
Here's two thousand seven hundred taels.

00:05:00.140 --> 00:05:01.020
Please keep it.

00:05:12.060 --> 00:05:13.979
Official Leopard Cat,

00:05:14.020 --> 00:05:16.020
leaving right after
collecting your winnings?

00:05:16.140 --> 00:05:18.139
That is not like you.

00:05:18.140 --> 00:05:19.338
Come, let us play a few rounds.

00:05:19.339 --> 00:05:21.338
- Yes.
- Indeed, stay for a few hands.

00:05:21.339 --> 00:05:23.260
Come on, a few more rounds.

00:05:28.179 --> 00:05:29.178
Come, come.

00:05:29.179 --> 00:05:29.778
Please sit.

00:05:29.779 --> 00:05:31.460
Sit, sit. Quickly.

00:05:37.700 --> 00:05:38.659
Stay calm.

00:05:38.979 --> 00:05:40.820
Let us see how they settle the deal.

00:05:42.900 --> 00:05:43.859
Official Tiger,

00:05:44.099 --> 00:05:46.299
five hundred taels. Please keep it.

00:05:46.380 --> 00:05:48.260
Nine to one split.

00:05:48.500 --> 00:05:50.780
That should be four hundred fifty taels.

00:05:51.099 --> 00:05:51.939
What?

00:05:51.940 --> 00:05:52.619
The rules changed?

00:05:52.620 --> 00:05:54.619
Oh, Official Tiger,

00:05:54.659 --> 00:05:55.939
that little girl

00:05:55.940 --> 00:05:58.099
could not hold on and passed away.

00:05:58.260 --> 00:05:59.178
So,

00:05:59.179 --> 00:06:00.861
we sold her body

00:06:00.862 --> 00:06:02.502
for a ghost marriage.

00:06:02.940 --> 00:06:04.379
That's why you get the money.

00:06:04.380 --> 00:06:04.858
Good, good.

00:06:04.859 --> 00:06:06.499
Ha! That is clever of you.

00:06:15.460 --> 00:06:16.459
Official Wolf,

00:06:16.460 --> 00:06:18.140
the one in your room

00:06:18.260 --> 00:06:19.178
is dying soon.

00:06:19.179 --> 00:06:21.259
Shall we arrange a ghost marriage
for her too?

00:06:21.260 --> 00:06:23.020
Go on, get lost.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:29.460
She seems to be one of the performers
who entered the Shengtang Guild with me.

00:06:30.539 --> 00:06:32.579
I will collect the selling fee later

00:06:32.580 --> 00:06:34.178
and share it with Official Wolf.

00:06:34.179 --> 00:06:35.939
Share the spoils?

00:06:35.940 --> 00:06:37.178
What spoils?

00:06:37.179 --> 00:06:38.778
We select talented women

00:06:38.779 --> 00:06:42.099
to give performers
across the realm a stage.

00:06:42.219 --> 00:06:43.298
Merchants and nobles

00:06:43.299 --> 00:06:44.911
generously support the grand feast.

00:06:44.912 --> 00:06:46.620
It is an elegant affair.

00:06:46.739 --> 00:06:47.259
Indeed.

00:06:47.260 --> 00:06:49.059
You are absolutely right.

00:06:49.060 --> 00:06:51.178
We will not disturb your pleasure then.

00:06:51.179 --> 00:06:52.899
If you need anything, just call me.

00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:54.260
Please enjoy yourselves.

00:07:01.620 --> 00:07:03.299
That is a lucrative post.

00:07:04.539 --> 00:07:07.418
In that case, I will take a hundred granaries
to aid the disaster victims.

00:07:07.419 --> 00:07:08.900
That will do nicely.

00:07:09.900 --> 00:07:11.739
Official Leopard Cat, what about you?

00:07:13.339 --> 00:07:14.978
Wealth and rank

00:07:14.979 --> 00:07:16.580
are not what I seek.

00:07:16.739 --> 00:07:17.979
I

00:07:19.339 --> 00:07:20.780
care only for beauty.

00:07:23.299 --> 00:07:24.820
So

00:07:25.979 --> 00:07:29.059
I want the Beauty Portrait in his hand.

00:07:37.179 --> 00:07:38.419
Official Leopard Cat,

00:07:38.659 --> 00:07:40.659
you must be joking.

00:07:41.299 --> 00:07:43.380
That Beauty Portrait
belongs to Lady Ruyi...

00:07:44.299 --> 00:07:44.859
No,

00:07:45.099 --> 00:07:46.582
it belongs to someone else.

00:07:46.739 --> 00:07:48.099
It is not to be coveted.

00:07:50.700 --> 00:07:53.460
Lady Ruyi's possessions
are naturally untouchable.

00:07:53.725 --> 00:07:56.178
But what belongs to others

00:07:56.179 --> 00:07:58.260
can be exchanged.

00:07:58.580 --> 00:07:59.870
For instance,

00:07:59.900 --> 00:08:02.059
this young lady.

00:08:02.100 --> 00:08:04.149
Since you have already
had your turn,

00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:05.858
why not make it cheaper

00:08:05.859 --> 00:08:06.924
and transfer her to me?

00:08:06.925 --> 00:08:08.813
Let me have a taste as well.

00:08:09.419 --> 00:08:10.419
Exactly.

00:08:19.739 --> 00:08:20.499
You

00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:21.882
should not have coveted her.

00:08:46.779 --> 00:08:47.739
Go.

00:08:51.100 --> 00:08:52.739
Every flower here

00:08:52.779 --> 00:08:54.895
represents a dead performer.

00:08:56.179 --> 00:08:57.739
Their pitiful souls

00:08:58.020 --> 00:08:59.660
will one day rise as flames

00:08:59.779 --> 00:09:01.782
and burn you in inferno.

00:09:34.100 --> 00:09:35.660
Help me!

00:10:11.299 --> 00:10:13.049
He stole my mask.

00:10:13.050 --> 00:10:15.691
- Go after him.
- Yes.

00:10:15.740 --> 00:10:17.060
Do not let them get away.

00:10:22.025 --> 00:10:24.386
♪After endless sorrow endured♪

00:10:24.387 --> 00:10:27.807
♪Love is a word too hard to sever♪

00:10:29.162 --> 00:10:32.924
♪Past ties fade like a dream gone cold♪

00:10:32.925 --> 00:10:35.736
♪In giving all, we found our only joy♪

00:10:35.737 --> 00:10:39.336
♪That year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms♪

00:10:39.337 --> 00:10:42.870
♪One night of snow
fell wild and restless♪

00:10:42.887 --> 00:10:48.995
♪Every perfect ending
hides a trace of regret♪

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:53.319
♪With blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell♪

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:57.640
♪No more longing will enter my dreams♪